📚 Why These Dependencies Matter
three
Provides the rendering engine, geometry tools, loaders, and materials.
Version 0.183+ ensures:

SVGLoader works correctly

ExtrudeGeometry is stable

WebGL2 features are available

TypeScript definitions match modern APIs

@react-three/fiber
The React renderer for Three.js.
Version 9.5+ ensures:

Correct JSX intrinsic element typing

Stable event system

Modern reconciler behavior

@react-three/drei
A curated set of helpers and abstractions.
Version 10.7+ ensures:

Updated loaders

Stable helpers

No deprecated APIs

@react-spring/core + @react-spring/three
Provides expressive, physics‑based animation.
Used for:

Hover effects

Click squash

Hologram pulses

Smooth transitions

postprocessing + @react-three/postprocessing
Required for:

Bloom

Glow

Hologram effects

Color grading

Depth‑based effects

zustand (optional)
Useful for:

Global UI state

Component communication

Theme and color palette state